    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable per ASME V&V 40 Table 4 at MRL 2. The assessment team acknowledges the Q3 2025 paediatric label expansion and has reviewed the extrapolation from adult validation data. Physical similarity arguments (monotonic shear-stress dependence, conservative bounding at 2.5 L/min) are judged sufficient to extend credibility to the paediatric sub-range (1.0–2.5 L/min) without additional experimental validation. The overall credibility package is accepted in support of the regulatory submission.",
